<h1>Where to look for game studies papers?<h1>

1. Digra: http://www.digra.org/) <br>
2. Game Studies: http://gamestudies.org/1602
3. Analog Game Studies: http://analoggamestudies.org/
4. University of Tampere Library (home of Internet and Game Studies, MSc): http://www.uta.fi/kirjasto/en/collections/theses.html

